0010 REM "IVR - Inventory Vendor Listing (Report Overlay)"
0020 REM "Program IVR.IB"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.2 - 01Jan97 |"
